snippet.title: Trollface Launch Playthrough
snippet.description:
Here is my first flash-game playthrough =) And also kind of a test-video. Trollface Launch is a fun little "launching" game. I´ll be doing more these kind of games in the future.

The game just basically ends, when you "should" get the super-upgrade. What an annoying ending xD
